msgid ""
"If the module was eagerly loaded, then this hook could simply instantiate "
"the module rather than fetching and compiling it as well. However, if the "
"eagerly loaded module is instantiated eagerly as well, the placeholder "
"functions will be patched out and never called in the first place, so this "
